RELEGATION PLAYOFFS:

Cabofriense - Volta Redonda

* On Apr 22, the local Sports' Court decided that no playoffs were needed, and that Cabofriense was
relegated.
* No dia 22/04, o TJD-RJ decidiu que não haveriam jogos extras, e que a Cabofriense seria
rebaixada.


